### QUESTS ###

when talking to an npc, check if a quest is being operated by the npc.
if the player is completing a quest by the npc, display a menu showing the start_msg and specific task.
add an option to talk to the npc normally, or leave

activate quests by talking to an npc, by going through specific dialogue
end quests by talking to the specfic npc

when an objective is complete, move on to the next one
objective types can be a node (when an event is created, it will send a node with info)
                       an item (return items to npc)

node types:
  get.item: checks if player picked up items
  kill.creature: checks when player kills a creature
  damage.creature: checks when player damages a creature, add damage to value
  explore.specific.location: checks when the player enters a location
  explore.new.location: checks when the player enters a location, and adds it to array if it doesnt exist. stores all areas, and can be used to check if player explored significant area
  buy.item
  sell.item
  craft.item
  talk.npc
  getxp.level
  getxp.skill.skillname